Package org.intermine.webservice.server Description

Intermine and mines derived from Intermine implement RESTfull web services. Current web services:
  • Query service - executes xml query specified in request and returns results.
  • List service - returns all public lists (bags) that contain object with specified id.
  • Template service - returns results of public template constrained with values in request.
